query:
SELECT ps.id, ps.colaborador, ps.cargo, ps.departamento, ps.reemplazo
FROM planes_sustitucion ps
WHERE ps.puestoClave = 'Si' 
  AND ps.id NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT planSustitucionId FROM planes_sucesion WHERE planSustitucionId IS NOT NULL)
ORDER BY ps.id DESC;
